<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">
<head>
	<meta charset="utf-8" />
	<title>받은선물 - GS25</title>
	<meta name="viewport" content="user-scalable=no, initial-scale=1.0, minimum-scale=1.0, maximum-scale=1.0, width=device-width, target-densitydpi=medium-dpi" />
	<meta name="format-detection" content="telephone=no,address=no,email=no" />
	<meta name="description" contents=""/>
	<meta name="keywords" contents=""/>
	<link rel="shortcut icon" type="image/x-icon" href="../images/favicon/favicon.ico">
	<link rel="apple-touch-icon" href="../images/favicon/favicon.png">
	<link rel="stylesheet" href="../../css/common.css">
	<script src="../../js/jquery-1.12.4.min.js"></script>
	<script src="../../js/plugin.js"></script>
	<script src="../../js/common.js"></script>
</head>

<body>
	<div class="skipMenu"><a href="#container">본문 바로가기</a></div>
	<div class="wrapper">
		<header class="header">
			<h1>받은선물</h1>
			<a href="#" class="btnBack">이전 페이지 이동</a>
		</header>
		<!-- //header -->
		<section id="container" class="content gs25">
            <!-- 내용 -->
			<!-- 선물정보 -->
			<div class="msgCard line">
				<ul class="infoData">
					<li><strong>보낸사람</strong><span><b>홍길동</b></span></li>
					<li><strong>전화번호</strong><span>01012345678</span></li>
					<li><strong>보낸일시</strong><span>2019-11-04</span></li>
				</ul>
				<div class="cardForm" style="background-image:url(../../image/tmp/img_card_thema.jpg)">
					<div class="giftBox">
						<div class="gInfo">
							<div class="img"><img src="../../image/tmp/img_tmp_giftcard.png" alt="대체 텍스트"></div>
							<strong class="tit">도시락 상품권 5천원권</strong>
							<div class="txt">
								<span role="text"><span class="hide">기한</span>2019-07-01까지</span>
								<span role="text"><span class="hide">수량</span>1개</span>
							</div>
						</div>
						<div class="gMsg">
							<p class="msg">안녕하세요. 힘내세요! 곧 좋은 일이 생길 거에요! 2020년에도 힘내세요!</p>
							<p class="from"><em>from</em> 박보검</p>
						</div>
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>
			<!-- //선물정보 -->
			<!-- 답장 -->
			<div class="msgCard line">
				<div class="titArea">
					<h2 class="titDep1">답장 보내기</h2>
				</div>
				<div class="cardForm reply">
					<div class="msgBox">
						<textarea class="msg" rows="6">감사메세지를 입력해 주세요.</textarea>
						<span class="cnt">한글 0/250자</span>
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>
			<!-- //답장 -->
			<ul class="notiInfo">
				<li>나만의 냉장고에서 선물받은 도시락 상품권은 나만의 냉장고에서 도시락 예약 주문 시에만 사용을 하실 수 있습니다.(점포에서 사용불가)</li>
			</ul>
			<div class="btnFixed">
				<div class="btnPrss">
					<button type="button" class="btnTP active">답장 보내기</button>
				</div>
			</div>
            <!--//내용 -->
		</section>
		<!-- //container -->
	</div>
	<!-- //wrapper -->
</body>
</html>

